      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，毫秒精度。那P1对应Education_LMS_Portal，P2是Education_StudentDB，P3还是回到Education_LMS_Portal对吧？我注意到P3里还有个T1_exec和T3_ULT是并行的？",
